// File: src/il/runtime/defs/api/core_crypto.def
// Purpose: Core, crypto, time, diagnostics, and process runtime functions.
// Key invariants:
//   - Included in declaration order by src/il/runtime/runtime.def.
//   - Class blocks remain balanced within this fragment.
// Ownership/Lifetime:
